sentences.english: A variety of conifers and hardwoods makes up the bulk of the vegetation .
sentences.chinese: 大部分植被由各种针叶树类和阔叶树类构成。

sentences.english: In some conifers adventitious roots can form the largest part of the root system.
sentences.chinese: 在一些针叶树不定根形成的根系统的最大部分。

sentences.english: As a rule, in the Northwest, these hosts are various kinds of conifer trees.
sentences.chinese: 作为一项规则，西北，这些主机是针叶树各种树木。

sentences.english: Bees produce a compound called propolis from the sap on needle-leaved trees or evergreens.
sentences.chinese: 蜜蜂利用针叶树或常绿植物的汁液制造蜂胶化合物。

sentences.english: The trouble is, other conifer eates didn't exhibit the same cancer.
sentences.chinese: 但问题是，其它吃针叶树的恐龙并没有患同样的癌症。

sentences.english: Coniferous chemical wood pulp, sulphite other than dissolving grades, unbleached.
sentences.chinese: 针叶树亚硫酸盐化学木浆，溶解级除外，未漂白。

sentences.english: The results indicated that the average water consumption rate of broadleaf trees was more than conifer trees.
sentences.chinese: 结果表明，针叶树种耗水速率低于阔叶树种。

sentences.english: In conifer orchards new stumps should be removed.
sentences.chinese: 在针叶树的种子园，新的伐桩应予除掉。

sentences.english: Conifer forests cover the eastern versant.
sentences.chinese: 东部山区被针叶树林覆盖。

sentences.english: The Baikushev's Pine is a coniferous tree from the species Bosnian Pine situated in Pirin, Bulgaria.
sentences.chinese: 百库西树是针叶树源于保加利亚波斯尼亚松物种。

sentences.english: Theoretic analysis for elastic modulus of softwood was carried out in this paper.
sentences.chinese: 本文是关于针叶树木材弹性特性研究的理论分析。

sentences.english: Cupressus of north temperate regions having dark scalelike leaves and rounded cones.
sentences.chinese: 北方温带柏科常绿针叶树，深色鳞状树叶，圆形球果。

sentences.english: On that piece of land I would also recommend conifers or maybe cedars.
sentences.chinese: 那块地嘛，我还建议你种引起针叶树，或许是雪松。

sentences.english: Non-coniferous chemical wood pulp, sulphite, other than dissolving grades, unbleached.
sentences.chinese: 非针叶树亚硫酸盐化学木浆，溶解级除外，未漂白。

sentences.english: The evergreens traditionally brought indoors were decorated with apples, symbolizing the Garden of Eden.
sentences.chinese: 传统上带入室内的针叶树用苹果装饰，象征着伊甸园。

sentences.english: It has been known that the self-sterility of conifers results from embryo collapse after self-fertilization.
sentences.chinese: 业已知道，针叶树自花不育是由于自花受精后胚凋萎。

definition: Masson pine (Pinus massoniana, Chinese red pine, horsetail pine)
tree, esp. with recognizable trunk (as opposed to 灌木[guan4 mu4], bush or shrub)
